  "metadata": {
    "description": "Trigify-powered social intelligence skills that give your AI agent access to the entire social web. Monitor competitors, track brand mentions, analyze content gaps, and surface buying signals across X, Reddit, YouTube, LinkedIn, Podcasts, and more.",
